  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Titenic is a Famicom beat-em-up based off of the 1997 film Titanic by ex-Hummer Team members. This game was hacked to create the more well-known Harry's Legend. The game was most probably first known to be on an ABAB 3-in-1 multicart and was later found on a 15-in-1 separated into two separate games.",
